和正面的地方.<br />\n所以呢套漫畫最有趣的地方,其實你並唔係睇緊果d故事,其實係面對緊自己的內心<br />\n<br />\n我相信作者之所將呢套漫畫取名為快樂人生,其實就係想道出:快樂並唔係有錢有女呢d咁膚淺野,細路仔都識講:人生不如意事十常八九,邊個做人唔會遇到不如意事,但最重要是你如何識得&quot;轉念&quot;,懂得一個正向思考,當你懂得呢點,你就掌握到快樂人生的關鍵<br />\n<br />\n當然以上只係我自己的理解,一百個人有一百個哈姆雷特,可能你睇完會有截然不同的領會"},{"pid":"d781d354b09914ddccc4c22962bc39afb85f2d93","tid":778023,"uid":57566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"三角草之春"},{"pid":"52506a9af7a5ae344a06743976df2aed8f45856d","tid":778023,"uid":72943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"自殺島"},{"pid":"52a7fdf8db4f6d992d14e118ab2061d5e73d831e","tid":778023,"uid":41434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"日在校園"},{"pid":"e030f2f69e8505e8118b74f48ffa233ca3d4ac1e","tid":778023,"uid":60432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"粉俠傳"},{"pid":"af3d9b7f2e717eecffae285da1d608d5e3786e4b","tid":778023,"uid":117552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"金田一"},{"pid":"e2da033f5a5e701adc5405897a1177b15182b8a0","tid":778023,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"deadpool"},{"pid":"628ac0d1bbd0717f39b4b0ff13b2c65d753521ea","tid":778023,"uid":29464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"輕羽飛揚"},{"pid":"1db87b640c209fa6ce87f61e0406fe547ac7bdd2","tid":778023,"uid":5320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"欺凌：高木同學"},{"pid":"18c9f3636686bb03c30635e8ede6210a1170d719","tid":778023,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"吸血大耳窿"},{"pid":"0d18bc93ac14c0373dbea2bc59c1e85daa4fd26d","tid":778023,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"邪神與廚二病少女 認真齊曬！"},{"pid":"a822c928d8e